item.description:
This is the perfect opportunity to come out and help plan out the year. We go over budget, current projects, ideas for future projects, and have fun while doing it. Dinner will be provided. If there is a project idea that you've been thinking of, bring it to this meeting with a layout of how much it will cost, supplies needed, etc.

If you can not make this meeting, but have an idea-submit the info to Caroline Winter at wintercl@gmail.com.

Hope you can make it out and I'm looking forward to hearing all the new ideas from our new members.
item.name: 2010 Chapter Planning Session
